# Reports

### Get price estimate
GET http://localhost:3000/reports?make=BMW&model=X5&year=2020&mileage=65000&lng=29.9187&lat=31.2001

### Create a report (requires signed-in session cookie)
POST http://localhost:3000/reports
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "make": "BMW",
  "model": "X5",
  "year": 2020,
  "mileage": 65000,
  "lng": 29.9187,
  "lat": 31.2001,
  "price": 950000
}

### Approve a report
PATCH http://localhost:3000/reports/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "approved": true
}
